name: Gateway to the Another Dimension
text:
Send 1 monster from your Deck / Extra Deck to your Graveyard and change the Level of all monsters on your field to the Level / Rank of the monster you have sent to the Graveyard. If you send a monster to your graveyard from your Deck, you can send 1 monster to your Graveyard from your hand.
This Skill will only activate if you begin the Duel with a Deck / Extra Deck contains no monsters other than "Chronomaly" monsters or LIGHT "Number" monsters.
